From: BORE CFS Upgrade v5 for Kernel 6.1 (v2 - Fixed)
Subject: [PATCH v2] sched: BORE upgrade - futex boost, hub/stub inheritance, burst preempt

v2: Fixed hunk failures in sched.h (KABI struct alignment),
    futex/waitwake.c (vendor hook context), features.h (SPDX header).

Upgrades existing inline CFS BORE (~v3.1.4) to v5 with:
- sched_burst_inherit_type (0=none, 1=parent, 2=hub/stub)
- Unified sched_burst_smoothness (0-3)
- Futex waiting boost
- Thread group burst inheritance
- Burst preemption via sched_bore & 2
- PREEMPT_SHORT_BORE feature
- Optimized defaults: offset=24, scale=1536, cache=75M

Signed-off-by: BORE Upgrade Patch v2
